name: OISEAU
description:
EAT SHRIMP. FEED THE BABY. BEST FEEDER WINS.

~MADE FOR #BARFCADE~

CONTROLS:

P1: WASD=move SPACE=barf

P2: ARROWS=move ENTER=barf

Tips n trix:

  • Hit the baby with the center of your barf ball for da most points
  • Larger Shrimp are worth more points
  • Popcorn Shrimp are worth more points at a smaller size
  • Cold Shrimp are best used in Shrimp cocktails or Shrimp cookies
  • OISEAU is french for BIRD
